_:N36ce88b4b4c547008cfea5c24bbfb8e6 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Baroness Twycross was appointed Baroness in Waiting (Government Whip) on 11 July 2024 and Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State at the Department for Culture, Media and Sport on 23 July 2024.</p>\n" .
